Class AirGroundReplacementProcessor.Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • robosky.structurehelpers.structure.processor.AirGroundReplacementProcessor.Entry
  • Enclosing class:
    AirGroundReplacementProcessor

    public static final class AirGroundReplacementProcessor.Entry
extends Object
    Replacement entry. A null air or ground value indicates not to place a block under that condition.
